On which exchange is Lydall's stock traded, what is its ticker symbol and CUSIP number?






                                               Lydall, Inc. common stock is listed on the New York Stock Exchange and trades under the symbol LDL, CUSIP number 550819106.
For more detailed stock information, please visit our Stock Quote page.
                                            






How can I buy Lydall stock? Can I buy stock directly from Lydall?






                                               Lydall stock can be bought through a stockbroker, bank, or other financial institutions that provide brokerage services. We do not currently have a plan in place to sell stock directly to the public.
                                            






Does Lydall pay a cash dividend on its stock? Does Lydall have a Dividend Reinvestment Program (DRIP)?






                                               Lydall does not currently pay a cash dividend on its common stock and does not anticipate doing so in the foreseeable future. Thus, there is no DRIP program in place. Lydall chooses to reinvest cash in its core businesses.
                                            






Whom do I contact with questions about transferring my stock?






                                               For stockholder inquiries regarding stock certificates, change of address, consolidation of accounts, transfer of ownership or other stock account matters, please contact our transfer agent:

Cindy Armenia
American Stock Transfer & Trust Company
6201 15th Avenue
Brooklyn, NY 11219
                                            






When was Lydall's initial public offering?






                                               A predecessor company, the Colonial Board Company, went public in 1963 and was traded on the NASDAQ system. In 1969, the name of the company was changed to Lydall, Inc.


                                            






Has Lydall had any stock splits?






                                               Below is the history of Lydall's stock splits.

Distribution DateFactor
June 19843 for 2
September 19912 for 1
September 19933 for 2
June 19952 for 1








In which year and where was Lydall incorporated?






                                               Lydall, originally incorporated in Connecticut, was reincorporated in Delaware in 1987.
                                            






Which firm of independent accountants audits Lydall?






                                               Lydall is audited by PricewaterhouseCoopers LLP in Hartford, Connecticut.
                                            






When is Lydall's fiscal year-end?







                                               Lydall's fiscal year-end is December 31.
                                            






